                                <span class="tag">System-Triggered</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded-lg flex items-center justify-between">
                                <div><strong class="block"><span class="lang-ar">وصول إشعار (Notification)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Notification arrives</span></strong><span class="text-sm opacity-60"><span class="lang-ar">اهتزاز بسيط (Shake) لجذب العين دون مقاطعة المهام.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">A simple shake to attract the eye without interrupting tasks.</span></span></div>
                                <span class="tag">System-Triggered</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 8 -->
        <section class="doc-container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span class="section-num en-font">SECTION 8.0</span>
                <h2 class="section-title"><span class="lang-ar">قانون الـ RTL للحركة الاتجاهية</span><span class="lang-en hidden">RTL law of directional motion</span></h2>
                <p class="section-desc">
                    <span class="lang-ar">في الواجهات العربية، القراءة تتدفق من اليمين إلى اليسار. بالتالي، محور زمن الحركة الاتجاهية (التقدم، التراجع، الدخول، الخروج) يجب أن يُعكس (Mirror) ليتوافق مع الإدراك البصري للمستخدم العربي.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">In Arabic interfaces, reading flows from right to left. Therefore, the time axis of the directional movement (advance, retreat, entry, exit) must be mirrored to match the visual perception of the Arab user.</span>
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <!-- Group A: Must Mirror -->
                <div class="bg-teal-50/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-teal-100">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-teal-900 mb-6 text-xl border-b border-teal-200 pb-2"><span class="lang-ar">حركات تُعكس إلزامياً (MUST Mirror)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Movements are mandatory mirrored (MUST Mirror)</span></h3>
                    <p class="text-sm opacity-80 mb-8"><span class="lang-ar">أي حركة تدل على التقدم في الزمن أو الاتجاهية أو الدخول الجانبي لمكونات تمتد مع النص.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Any movement indicates progress in time, directionality, or lateral entry of components that extend with the text.</span></p>
                    
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                            <span class="font-bold"><span class="lang-ar">أشرطة التقدم (Progress Bars)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Progress Bars</span></span>
                            <div class="w-1/2 h-2 bg-gray-200 rounded overflow-hidden" dir="rtl">
                                <div class="w-full h-full bg-teal-500 animate-[progress_2s_infinite]"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                            <span class="font-bold"><span class="lang-ar">انتقال الخطوات (Step Flows)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Step Flows</span></span>
                            <div class="flex gap-2">
                                <i data-lucide="arrow-left" class="animate-pulse text-teal-600"></i>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                            <span class="font-bold"><span class="lang-ar">الأدراج (Drawers)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Drawers</span></span>
                            <span class="text-xs en-font bg-white px-2 py-1 rounded border">Enter from Right</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Group B: Do NOT Mirror -->
                <div class="bg-gray-100 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 text-xl border-b border-gray-300 pb-2"><span class="lang-ar">حركات لا يجوز عكسها (Do NOT Mirror)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Movements that may not be reversed (Do NOT Mirror)</span></h3>
                    <p class="text-sm opacity-80 mb-8"><span class="lang-ar">الحركات القائمة على قوانين دوران فيزيائية عالمية غير مرتبطة باتجاه لغة القراءة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Movements based on universal physical rotation laws are not related to the direction of the reading language.</span></p>
                    
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                            <span class="font-bold"><span class="lang-ar">التحديث الدائري (Refresh)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Circular Refresh</span></span>
                            <i data-lucide="loader-2" class="animate-spin text-gray-500"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                            <span class="font-bold"><span class="lang-ar">عقارب الساعة (Clock)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Clock</span></span>
                            <i data-lucide="clock" class="text-gray-500"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                            <span class="font-bold"><span class="lang-ar">عناصر التحكم بالوسائط</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Media controls</span></span>
                            <div class="flex gap-1" dir="ltr">
                                <i data-lucide="play" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current text-gray-500"></i>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <style>
                @keyframes progress { 0% { width: 0%; } 100% { width: 100%; } }
            </style>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 9 -->
        <section class="bg-gray-50 border-y border-gray-200">
            <div class="doc-container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="section-num en-font">SECTION 9.0</span>
                    <h2 class="section-title"><span class="lang-ar">أمثلة تطبيقية (UI Component Motion)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Application examples (UI Component Motion)</span></h2>
                    <p class="section-desc"><span class="lang-ar">عينات موثقة لطبيعة الحركة في المكونات الأكثر تفاعلاً.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Documented samples of the nature of movement in the most reactive components.</span></p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                    <!-- Siniya Concept -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden group">
                        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent to-orange-50/50 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 motion-slow"></div>
                        <span class="tag absolute top-4 left-4 z-10">Micro-interaction sequence</span>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 relative z-10 text-orange-800"><span class="lang-ar">الصينية التفاعلية (Interactive Siniya)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Interactive Siniya</span></h3>
                        <p class="text-sm opacity-70 mb-8 relative z-10"><span class="lang-ar">بديلاً عن سلة التسوق الجامدة. عند أضافة صنف: (1) ينكمش الزر كتأكيد، (2) يهبط أيقون مرئي بانحناء نحو الصينية السفلية، (3) تقوم الصينية بقفزة احتفالية خفيفة وناعمة جداً.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">An alternative to the rigid shopping cart. When an item is added: (1) the button shrinks as confirmation, (2) a visual icon descends in a curtsey towards the bottom tray, (3) the tray makes a very soft and light celebratory jump.</span></p>
                        
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6 relative z-10 h-40 justify-center">
                            <!-- Redesigned Siniya: Silver Circle, Larger, Falcon Perspective -->
                            <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[#D1D5DB] via-[#9CA3AF] to-[#6B7280] shadow-2xl border-2 border-[#E5E7EB] flex items-center justify-center relative group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform motion-base overflow-hidden">
                               <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_30%_30%,rgba(255,255,255,0.4),transparent)]"></div>
                               <div class="w-28 h-28 rounded-full border border-white/20"></div>
                               <!-- Hover Badge -->
                               <span class="bg-gray-800 text-white text-[10px] en-font font-bold w-5 h-5 rounded-full absolute top-4 right-4 flex items-center justify-center transform scale-0 group-hover:scale-100 transition-transform delay-150">1</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Modal Entrance -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden group cursor-pointer">
                        <span class="tag absolute top-4 left-4 z-10">Scale & Opacity</span>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 relative z-10"><span class="lang-ar">النوافذ المنبثقة (Modals)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Pop-ups (Modals)</span></h3>
                        <p class="text-sm opacity-70 mb-8 relative z-10"><span class="lang-ar">لا تظهر فجأة. تدخل النوافذ من وضعية تصغير وتشفيف (Scale 95%, Opacity 0%) إلى حجمها الطبيعي، لمحاكاة الاقتراب من عدسة الكاميرا، وبتوقيت (Slow / 500ms).</span><span class="lang-en hidden">It doesn't appear suddenly. The windows go from reduced and blurred (Scale 95%, Opacity 0%) to their normal size, to simulate approaching the camera lens, and with a timing of (Slow / 500ms).</span></p>
                        
                        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gray-900/40 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 motion-slow z-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                            <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-2xl w-3/4 opacity-0 transform scale-95 translate-y-4 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-100 group-hover:translate-y-0 motion-slow">
                                <div class="w-1/3 h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded mb-2"></div>
                                <div class="w-full h-8 bg-gray-100 rounded"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 10 -->
        <section class="doc-container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span class="section-num en-font">SECTION 10.0</span>
                <h2 class="section-title"><span class="lang-ar">السرد القصصي عبر التمرير (Scroll Storytelling)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Scroll Storytelling</span></h2>
                <p class="section-desc">
                    <span class="lang-ar">التمرير ليس وسيلة تنقل فحسب، بل هو "ناظم للإيقاع السردي". نستخدم تأثيرات التمرير لكشف المحتوى تصاعدياً، مما يمنح إحساساً بالعمق والفخامة، شريطة أن تظل هادئة وغير استعراضية (Theatrical).</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Scrolling is not only a means of navigation, but also a “regulator of narrative rhythm.” We use scrolling effects to unfold the content incrementally, giving a sense of depth and grandeur, provided it remains quiet and non-theatrical.</span>
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-[#2B1A14] text-white p-12 rounded-2xl relative overflow-hidden group">
                <div class="max-w-md relative z-10 space-y-8">
                    <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-xl transform translate-y-4 opacity-50 group-hover:translate-y-0 group-hover:opacity-100 motion-slow">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2 text-[#F4A261]"><span class="lang-ar">اكتشاف تدريجي</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Gradual discovery</span></h4>
                        <p class="text-sm opacity-80"><span class="lang-ar">تظهر الطبقات من الأسفل إلى الأعلى وتكتسب شفافية كاملة أثناء مرور المستخدم، للتركيز على رسالة واحدة في كل مرة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Layers appear from the bottom up and gain full transparency as the user scrolls, to focus on one message at a time.</span></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-xl transform translate-y-8 opacity-0 group-hover:translate-y-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-700 ease-out delay-150">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2"><span class="lang-ar">بارالاكس مُهذب (Mild Parallax)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Mild Parallax</span></h4>
                        <p class="text-sm opacity-80"><span class="lang-ar">حركة بسيطة بطيئة للخلفيات لا تتجاوز مسافات قصيرة لإضفاء عمق مكاني رقيق للغاية محصور على الصور الفوتوغرافية.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Simple, slow movement of backgrounds over short distances to give photographs a very subtle spatial depth.</span></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Abstract Parallax BG -->
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIyMCIgaGVpZ2h0PSIyMCI+PGNpcmNsZSBjeD0iMiIgY3k9IjIiIHI9IjEiIGZpbGw9InJnYmEoMjU1LDI1NSwyNTUsMC4wNSkiLz48L3N2Zz4=')] opacity-50 transform scale-110 group-hover:scale-100 transition-transform duration-[2s] ease-out"></div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 11 -->
        <section class="bg-gray-50 border-y border-gray-200">
            <div class="doc-container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="section-num en-font">SECTION 11.0</span>
                    <h2 class="section-title"><span class="lang-ar">حالات التحميل المطمئنة (Loading States)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Reassuring Loading States</span></h2>
                    <p class="section-desc">
                        <span class="lang-ar">المؤشرات الدوارة (Spinners) العشوائية تستدعي القلق وتعطي إحساساً بطول الانتظار. يُكتفى باستخدام مؤشرات الهياكل العظمية (Skeleton Screens) الوامضة التي تحاكي الشكل النهائي للمحتوى القادم، مما يقلل "الزمن المُدرك" للانتظار بنسبة كبيرة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Random spinning indicators cause anxiety and give a feeling of long waiting. Only flashing Skeleton Screens are used to mimic the final appearance of upcoming content, significantly reducing the “perceived wait time”.</span>
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center">
                    <div class="w-full bg-white border border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm mb-4">
                        <div class="flex gap-4 items-center">
                            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-lg skeleton"></div>
                            <div class="flex-1 space-y-3">
                                <div class="h-4 w-3/4 skeleton rounded"></div>
                                <div class="h-3 w-1/2 skeleton rounded"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-xs en-font text-gray-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Shimmer Pulse (Infinite loop until data arrives)</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 12 -->
        <section class="doc-container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span class="section-num en-font">SECTION 12.0</span>
                <h2 class="section-title text-red-800"><span class="lang-ar">قانون الانضباط وإمكانية الوصول (Restraint Law)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Discipline and Accessibility Law</span></h2>
                <p class="section-desc">
                    <span class="lang-ar">الحركة الاستعراضية التي لا تخدم غرضاً وظيفياً تُعد عبئاً إدراكياً وتُمنع تماماً. علاوة على ذلك، النظام يتوافق إلزامياً مع طلبات تقليل الحركة من أنظمة التشغيل.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Exhibitive movement that does not serve a functional purpose is considered a cognitive burden and is strictly prohibited. Furthermore, the system obligatorily complies with motion reduction requests from operating systems.</span>
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center bg-red-50/30 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-red-100">
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-red-900 mb-4"><span class="lang-ar">حالة النظام المُخفّض للحركة</span><span class="lang-en hidden">State of the reduced motion system</span><br><span class="en-font text-sm opacity-60">(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)</span></h3>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-sm opacity-90 text-gray-800">
                        <li><span class="lang-ar">يتم إلغاء تأثير البارالاكس تماماً.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The effect of Paralax is completely eliminated.</span></li>
                        <li><span class="lang-ar">يتم تحويل انتقالات المكونات المكانية (Sliding) إلى انتقالات شفافة (Fade).</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Spatial component transitions (Sliding) are converted to transparent transitions (Fade).</span></li>
                        <li><span class="lang-ar">إلغاء التكبير والتصغير (Scaling) في النوافذ المنبثقة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Cancel zooming and zooming in pop-up windows.</span></li>
                        <li><span class="lang-ar">إيقاف الومضات اللانهائية القوية وتخفيفها.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Stop and reduce the endless intense flashes.</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <!-- Visual mock of reduced motion -->
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-center text-sm">
                    <div class="bg-white border rounded p-4 opacity-50"><i data-lucide="x" class="mx-auto mb-2 text-red-500"></i><span class="lang-ar">لا انزلاقات</span><span class="lang-en hidden">No slips</span></div>
                    <div class="bg-white border rounded p-4 opacity-50"><i data-lucide="x" class="mx-auto mb-2 text-red-500"></i><span class="lang-ar">لا تكبير استعراضي</span><span class="lang-en hidden">No show zoom</span></div>
                    <div class="bg-white border text-green-800 font-bold border-green-200 rounded p-4 bg-green-50 col-span-2 flex items-center justify-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="text-green-600"></i><span class="lang-ar">تغير بشفافية العتامة (Opacity) فقط</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Change the transparency and opacity only</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 13 & 14 -->
        <section class="bg-gray-900 text-white mt-12 py-20">
            <div class="doc-container">
                <div class="max-w-3xl mb-12">
                    <span class="section-num en-font text-gray-400">SECTION 13.0 & 14.0</span>
                    <h2 class="section-title"><span class="lang-ar">ملخص النظام والقيود النهائية</span><span class="lang-en hidden">System summary and final restrictions</span></h2>
                </div>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/10">
                        <i data-lucide="fingerprint" class="text-teal-400 mb-4 opacity-80"></i>
                        <h4 class="font-bold mb-2"><span class="lang-ar">القصدية الصارمة</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Strict intentionality</span></h4>
                        <p class="text-xs opacity-70 leading-relaxed"><span class="lang-ar">الحركة يجب أن تكون مقصودة وليست زينة. كل حركة تبدأ بمسبب واضح (Trigger) وتوفر تأكيداً (Feedback).</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Movement should be intentional, not decorative. Every movement begins with a clear trigger (Trigger) and provides confirmation (Feedback).</span></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/10">
                        <i data-lucide="hourglass" class="text-amber-400 mb-4 opacity-80"></i>
                        <h4 class="font-bold mb-2"><span class="lang-ar">النظام الزمني الموحد</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Unified time system</span></h4>
                        <p class="text-xs opacity-70 leading-relaxed"><span class="lang-ar">ممنوع استخدام أزمنة عشوائية. الالتزام المطلق بـ 3 مستويات: سريع (150ms)، قياسي (300ms)، بطيء (500ms).</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Do not use random tenses. Absolute commitment with 3 levels: fast (150ms), standard (300ms), slow (500ms).</span></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/10">
                        <i data-lucide="move-right" class="text-blue-400 mb-4 opacity-80 transform rotate-180"></i>
                        <h4 class="font-bold mb-2"><span class="lang-ar">الانسجام الثقافي (RTL)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Cultural Harmony (RTL)</span></h4>
                        <p class="text-xs opacity-70 leading-relaxed"><span class="lang-ar">عكس الحركات الاتجاهية للتوافق مع دفق قراءة الواجهة العربية من اليمين إلى اليسار تلقائياً.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Automatically reverse the directional movements to match the flow of reading the Arabic interface from right to left.</span></p>
